### Initialize stock
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/stock
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productId": 1,
  "variantId": null,
  "quantity": 50,
  "lowStockThreshold": 5
}

### Get stock by product
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/stock/product/1

### Low stock items
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/stock/low-stock
